967
01:06:47.754 --> 01:06:49.963
Voi fi vinul tău.

968
01:06:54.594 --> 01:06:56.220
Are gânduri secundare.

969
01:06:59.182 --> 01:07:00.432
Nu pot.

970
01:07:01.100 --> 01:07:02.768
